text: Metasulenus unicolor is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae, and the only species in the genus Metasulenus. It was described by Breuning in 1970.Biolib.cz - Metasulenus unicolor. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphorini Category:Beetles described in 1970
title: Metasulenus unicolor
